{"tid":850663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【街霸重臨】代理與地監職員起衝突 有人被一拳KO","createTime":"2018-10-06T15:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T16:04:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"882f51199cadee82ec4cb021db7a6a08226e681f","tid":850663,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58764462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764462&d=bbj2SoGVaOb6bYcrjj93nhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2606421a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764462&h=feacc1a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58764462</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月06日 <br />\n<br />\n【街霸重臨】代理與地監職員起衝突 有人被一拳KO<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1006 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538819382_3163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538819382_3163.jpg&h=f9cb96ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒地人士由傍人扶起（照片由現場代理提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【更新地監局回應】<br />\n<br />\n近期二手市場冰封，大批代理無單開要轉戰一手新盤搶客。<br />\n<br />\n位於太子始創中心，九建油塘海傲灣售樓處門外，有人目睹，現場地產代理與現場監察的地監局職員起衝突，居然一拳將該名地監局人員揮低，令他受傷倒地。其後警員到場，該名打人者被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n地監局回應指，有關事件已交警方依法處理，而監管局亦會跟進個案，任何被證實於執業期間涉及暴力案件而被定罪的地產代理，除了會留有案底之外，亦會被監管局撤銷牌照，而有關人士所屬的地產代理公司，亦有可能因沒有妥善管理其員工操守而被處分。<br />\n<br />\n監管局已聯絡有關樓盤的發展商作出跟進，改善有關銷售處的秩序安排，而本局人員會繼續堅守於一手住宅物業銷售處進行巡查工作，並會適當地增加人手安排。監管局譴責任何不法使用暴力的行為，並強調絕不容忍任何害群之馬，嚴重損害地產代理業界之形象。<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳寶恩<br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=bbj2SoGVaOb6bYcrjj93nhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=4905e9b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538818839_a671.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538818839_a671.jpg&h=b6f64969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人倒地（照片由現場代理提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538820357_af57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538820357_af57.jpg&h=1b22cb13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到場拘捕打人者（現場人士提供）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【魑魅魍魎】羅康瑞，一生也在爭爭搶搶（十一少）<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【油塘新盤】九建：海傲灣最快下周開售"},{"pid":"ab483ba99f929224498a5c17edb715d0663890e0","tid":850663,"uid":31507,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母明明係地監屈人，正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6910ccb10f27c1a9223f4d6a395ff17509323478","tid":850663,"uid":8294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"打政府職員仲要喺咁近旺角警署嘅地方開波<br />\n冇腦即係冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7ac5be12d1a3163ac5f3299aab1386c0290b49","tid":850663,"uid":28599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab483ba99f929224498a5c17edb715d0663890e0","tid":850663,"uid":31507,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T15:58:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母明明係地監屈人，正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit